oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Billy Block's Western Beat American Music Showcase (Jan. 7)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Ciambotti, Gia; Walmsley, Jon; Metal photoplates;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (blue and silver on white) announcing Billy Block's Western Beat American Music Showcase featuring Jenny Yates, Dylan O'Brian, Gia Ciambotti, Mel Harker, Alfred Johnson, Jon Walmsley, Tex Beamont and Gary Floyd hosted by Teresa James and Terry Wilson at Highland Grounds on January 7. Poster features metal photoplates of dancers and Billy Block's Western Beat logo.
